<h2>Install</h2>

<p>This layout mode is not included in <a href="../isotope.pkgd.js">isotope.pkgd.js</a> and must be installed separately.</p>

<p><a href="https://raw.github.com/metafizzy/isotope-horizontal/master/horizontal.js">Download horizontal.js on GitHub</a>.</p>

<p>Install with Bower:</p>

``` bash
bower install isotope-horizontal
```

<p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/isotope-horizontal">Install with npm</a>:</p>

``` bash
npm install isotope-horizontal
```


<h1>Options</h1>


<h2>verticalAlignment</h2>

<div class="param">
  <p class="param-bit type">
    <b>Type:</b>
    <span class="value"><i>Number</i> a decimal 0 to 1</span>
  </p>
</div>

<p>Aligns items vertically. <code>0</code> will align the origin edge. <code>1</code> will align the opposite edge. <code>0.5</code> will align center.</p>

<div class="example">
  <div class="example__code">
    ``` js
    layoutMode: 'horizontal',
    horizontal: {
      verticalAlignment: 0.5,
    }
    ```
  </div>
